reviewText: It's a shame that Richard Lynch so often plays a  ruthless killer - but he does it so damn good !. And he's especially nasty in this low-budget production. -I haven't seen him this cruel since "Invasion  U.S.A.". There's not much of a story, but who cares; if you're a Lynch  fan you'll want it no matter what, ofcourse. It's a crazy price, hopefully  it'll go down soon.
